      rationale: "Verified current requirements/project.md:7 reads 'Distributed CLI-first as a non-editable wheel installed from a tag-pinned git URL... cloning or forking the repo remains a secondary path for advanced users who want to modify the source.' This text already reads as installer-primary/forker-secondary, supporting the F-12 = drop decision. The line content does support 'already balanced.'"
