    - finding_index: 7
      rationale: "cli.py:268 stderr being conditional is correct, but criticality 'high' is supported by other factors enumerated in the assessment: CLAUDE.md edits affect the load-bearing project-context file all agents read; bin/cortex-check-parity is a drift-prone enforcement gate; cross-references span 9+ files where a wrong path would cascade. The cli.py-specific argument is one of several supports, not the sole load-bearing one."
    - finding_index: 8
