    - finding_index: 9
      rationale: "Round-2 scope expansions (docs/backlog.md trim with plugin-development.md migration, broader SKILL file sweep, code-reference updates) were ratified by the user via commit c019e97 'Consolidate #166+#167 and apply round 2 audit findings' — the recent consolidation commit. Dashboard policy IS in parent epic scope per backlog/165...md:48 'cortex dashboard verb policy: ship verb / flag contributor-only / cut docs/dashboard.md from installer index — child #166.' The other expansions are intentional."
